Training Master
Yagyu, the training master in the Kerei guildhouse, offers guidance
and assigns the unique <marks> that raise Ninja guild level. Ask him to
"accept challenge", "list challenge", or "reroll challenge". Each
assignment permits one free reroll, and neither assignment nor completion
costs experience or GXP. He is the formal trainer for the order, even for
Ninja who entered through the hidden Darkwind rooms.
